{"tid":561301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「美國夏蕙姨」77歲整容富婆待嫁　未婚夫：她像16歲少女","createTime":"2018-02-15T01:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T03:24:41.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"483161819c28221d87992001900718eb45831bbb","tid":561301,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:21:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180215/640_f85e34685dee8e89cbd334479c97b7e9.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180215%2F640_f85e34685dee8e89cbd334479c97b7e9.jpg&d=f9NUqfofeIko5MxKqjpakARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=588f3338\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180215/640_f85e34685dee8e89cbd334479c97b7e9.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n情人眼裡出西施！在時裝設計師男友克萊因（Lloyd Klein）眼中，有「美國夏蕙姨」（夏蕙姨即香港息影藝人黃夏蕙）之稱的77歲億萬富婆懷得斯頓（Jocelyn Wildenstein），外貌與16歲青春少女一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n77歲的懷得斯頓20年來首次接受電視訪問，與50歲未婚夫克萊因粉墨登場。懷得斯頓一雙向上吊的眼睛、奇怪臉形加上腫脹雙唇，過去多年都被人指是整容失敗，也為她帶來「貓女」的稱號。<br />\n<br />\n克萊因全力為愛侶護航，他說：「通常我們去餐廳或一些法國地方，他們會說：『你好，碧姬。』我就會說：『事實上，你真的長得像碧姬芭杜（Brigitte Bardot）。』」碧姬芭杜是法國早年的性感女神，當年憑天使臉孔魔鬼身材俘虜世上男女。克萊因還說：「她（懷得斯頓）從沒做任何事改變面容。我有她16歲的照片，她看來與今天一模一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n被問是否整過容，懷得斯頓直接了當回答：「沒有。特別是當我們回顧我的照片時。當然，也許那時我比較美麗。當我們年輕時，我們有某種新鮮感，新鮮感隨歲月流逝，但你仍找到同一雙眼、一樣高的顴骨或一樣的鼻。」懷得斯頓自言：「我總是看來像碧姬芭杜。」<br />\n<br />\n克萊因說：「看，懷得斯頓是美麗的，是奇妙的。第一次見她，我就被她的美貌、雙眼及性格迷住。我在時裝界工作，見過所有超模，見過所有人，見過天橋上最美麗的女人。但懷得斯頓有種不是太多女人有的魅力。」<br />\n<br />\n懷得斯頓1999年與出軌的法國藝術收藏家丈夫維登斯坦（Alec Wildenstein）離婚，雙方達成協議，懷得斯頓獲25億美元（約738億元台幣）的天價離婚費，讓她成為全球頭條人物。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180215/640_17fe9997f22aa5f0d380adab0608d7bd.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180215%2F640_17fe9997f22aa5f0d380adab0608d7bd.jpg&d=f9NUqfofeIko5MxKqjpakARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c3e256f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180215/640_17fe9997f22aa5f0d380adab0608d7bd.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75973eab926b166d8ac45641a816fb6f29b46c3f","tid":561301,"uid":5303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:26:09.000Z","msg":"Joker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0cf62636dedfe2341702cf0d8aa6eb2052b3bb","tid":561301,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:27:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1887a1df88d075b90eefe426dd6d0455b8bef740","tid":561301,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:30:17.000Z","msg":"希望富婆長命百歲"},{"pid":"74b79702ab1b94cf1423cd61b21ccf42bfddbc37","tid":561301,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:31:11.000Z","msg":"為了錢，有咩哽唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e203038df53d7930f7e2b6d3df267ae8186010a","tid":561301,"uid":47966,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:32:13.000Z","msg":"樓豬冇貼圖，全家平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d32ad27c7e923993e9ec365cb8c02c1468a0be0","tid":561301,"uid":50101,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:32:14.000Z","msg":"淨係貼link 都算你有點良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18d7485cb9e9de12e9405400a46153bc34d2fd5","tid":561301,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:33:13.000Z","msg":"佢老公話緊佢智商？"},{"pid":"8692d314eff1b24d96f97cfd141468ace96eb479","tid":561301,"uid":35644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:33:31.000Z","msg":"屌 嚇鳩死"},{"pid":"313f499b6ab377cab2002b69f2c3e9dce450c061","tid":561301,"uid":122217,"lik